    "name": "Hexworm",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Hexworm",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "These gray larvae inch across the ground with an instinct to feed on magic.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Howl of the Wild",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Howl of the Wild pg. 159",
                        "alt": "Howl of the Wild pg. 159",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 226
                    },
                    "page": 159,
                    "errata": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "2.1",
                        "alt": "2.1",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 226
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Hexmoth",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "At first glance, hexworms appear to be nondescript grubs, but their ability to sense and consume magic quickly becomes clear. They grow rapidly, devouring the power in witches' huts, arcanists' studies, and magical glades at an alarming rate before spinning cocoons and emerging as beautiful, varied hexmoths. Some have a taste for particular types of magic, like fire spells or primal magic.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Howl of the Wild",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Howl of the Wild pg. 159",
                        "alt": "Howl of the Wild pg. 159",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 226
                    },
                    "page": 159,
                    "errata": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "2.1",
                        "alt": "2.1",
